title: BLM Wilderness Areas for the State of Colorado (Polygon)
name: BLM Wilderness Areas for the State of Colorado (Polygon)
description:
This data set consist of digital data describing BLM Wilderness Area (WLD)
Boundaries for the State of Colorado. The data set includes 1:24,000 wld maps
from BLM District Montrose. At this time BLM type wilderness only exsist in
this former District.

Data set is projected into UTM zone 13. Individual coverages were merged into a single coverage.
The file was checked for polygon topology, dangles, and slivers. Any errors
of this kind were corrected before creating the E00 ArcInfo interchange
file.

For more information on the FGDC standard, example metadata,
and metadata tools, see:
<URL:http://www.fgdc.gov/Metadata/Metadata.html>
